    { "native": "체크인 할게요", "transliteration": "chekeuin halgeyo", "english": "I'd like to check in", "pronunciation": "cheh-keu-een hahl-geh-yo", "formality": "neutral", "tip": "Check-out is 체크아웃 (chekeuaut)." },
